  description: "Kasnor is the main leisure hub of Chronosant, it is an island that
    is in the middle of an ocean with calm beaches and a tropical climate. As Chorosant
    grew more and more. Kasnor was made a nature reserve where no building is allowed.
    As such, it is one of the only parts of the planet where natural beauty isn\u2019t
    obscured by vast, sprawling cities."
